query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from site AS s
inner join tag AS t
on t.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('ell') AND t.name IN ('adjectives',
'adverbs',
'modal-verbs',
'past-tense',
'questions',
'sentence-structure',
'vocabulary')
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND tq.site_id = s.site_id
inner join question AS q
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND q.score >= 0 AND q.score <= 1000;
